Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.01,0:02:35.01,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}#4　　合宿!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
