Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.59,0:03:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  馬上就要到暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道要去海邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是爬山？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是樂隊的集訓合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從早到晚都要好好練習！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.15,0:03:24.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  得買好穿的衣服才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳裝也要買啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說！
